on of large Reynolds\nnumber while the amplitude of turbulence can still be small.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Nov 2015 16:35:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 29 Nov 2015 15:28:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-05-25"}
