ple attractors; and (4) The large predator population using the\npassive dispersal could lead to no interior equilibrium but both prey and\npredator can coexist through fluctuating dynamics for almost all initial\nconditions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Nov 2015 18:18:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 17 Nov 2015 07:02:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-11-18"}
