ion rate is maintained for several\nGyr, a large fraction of the stars in present-day bulges likely formed in-situ.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Nov 2015 21:00:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-01-27"}
